   <div class="article-head"> 
    <h2>法国警察持老式步枪保卫巴黎 实为中国最缺警枪</h2> 
    <p class="info"> <span>2013/11/21 3:36:00</span><span>作者:admin</span><span>点击数:(<font color="red"><font type="showhits" action="count" f="0" id="3613" t="1">0</font></font>)</span><span>评论:<font color="red"><font type="showhits" action="cmtnum" f="0" id="3613" t="1">0</font></font></span> 
